arketing billboards and experiential retail. Their Well Collective concept =
stores, for instance, transform traditional retail spaces into wellness hub=
s where customers can explore fitness journeys through interactive digital =
experiences=E2=80=94and, of course, still pick up their online orders in-st=
ore. Hill gets this.<br/>=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;
margin-bottom:0px;">He=E2=80=99s already rebuilding bridges with key wholes=
ale partners, like Dick=E2=80=99s and Foot Locker. During a recent channel =
