 Foot Locker, including an entire annex room, =E2=80=9CHouse of Hoops,=E2=
=80=9D that felt like a shrine to Jordans. After being notably absent for a=
 spell from The Running Event, an industry-wide trade show in San Antonio, =
Nike strategically returned this year with a shoe that seems to have learne=
d a thing
or two from its competitors. The <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJ=
